law.text: The salaries of county commissioners, payable by their respective counties in full for all services performed by said commissioners except as otherwise provided, shall be as follows:— Middlesex..... $9,505.16 Essex..... 8,799.73 Norfolk..... 8,799.73 Worcester..... 8,799.73 Bristol..... 7,388.87 Hampden..... 7,388.87 Barnstable..... 6,683.44 Berkshire..... 6,683.44 Plymouth..... 6,683.44 Franklin..... 5,272.58 Hampshire..... 5,272.58 Dukes..... 2,963.90
